title: STAT+: Pharmacy compounder files antitrust lawsuit against Eli Lilly and Novo Nordisk
description: A compounding pharmacy has filed a lawsuit accusing Eli Lilly and Novo Nordisk of using anticompetitive tactics to prevent it from serving patients.
